00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:34,758
将由48岁的Bart McDade代替Gregory的位子
replacing Gregory with 48-year-old Bart McDade

209
00:10:34,758 --> 00:10:38,095
Bart McDade 雷曼兄弟新总裁兼首席运营官

210
00:10:34,843 --> 00:10:38,095
这是他所做过的最艰难的一个决定
has been one of the most difficult decisions he's had to make.

211
00:10:39,806 --> 00:10:42,558
Dick 韩国人刚刚到达Sullivan
Dick, the Koreans just arrived at Sullivan.

212
00:10:43,685 --> 00:10:44,852
我们一定要抓住这次机会
Let's go make this happen.

213
00:10:45,395 --> 00:10:47,730
我觉得这会儿你最好就待在这里
My take is you'd be better off staying here for now.

214
00:10:49,566 --> 00:10:51,358
我们要把你打造成为"幕后人士"
We need you to be our "missing man."

215
00:10:51,901 --> 00:10:54,320
由我们去谈 尽最大努力去促成这笔交易
We'll go in and push the deal as far as we can,

216
00:10:54,404 --> 00:10:57,990
最后再由你出面来达成这笔交易
and then we'll bring you in at the end to top it off.

217
00:10:58,158 --> 00:10:59,408
好吧 听你的
All right, fine.

218
00:11:00,535 --> 00:11:02,328
很好
Okay. Okay.

219
00:11:07,917 --> 00:11:10,544
我们如期来到了纽约
We are committed to our presence in New York.

220
00:11:12,881 --> 00:11:15,924
但我们需要知道确切的数字
But we need to know that the underlying numbers make sense.

221
00:11:19,262 --> 00:11:21,930
我们也看到了事情的发展情况
We realize how things look.

222
00:11:22,015 --> 00:11:24,224
但我们的股价只是被一些做空者暂时挫伤
But our stock is getting hammered by the shorts.

223
00:11:24,642 --> 00:11:26,101
它的真实价值依旧没变
The value is still there.

224
00:11:28,104 --> 00:11:31,565
我们刚刚开始谈 Min还是很兴奋的 但他们还没有给出具体的数字
We just started. Min's excited, but we haven't heard the terms.

225
00:11:33,151 --> 00:11:34,234
你在哪儿?
Where are you?

226
00:11:34,319 --> 00:11:35,944
我刚走出会议室来接你的电话啊
I just stepped out to take the call.

227
00:11:36,821 --> 00:11:38,489
快回去 要有礼貌啊
Get back in there. Don't be rude.

228
00:11:39,783 --> 00:11:41,575
好的
Okay.

229
00:11:41,659 --> 00:11:44,495
我们只是将你们不感兴趣的那一部分资产
We simply take the assets you don't find appealing,

230
00:11:45,538 --> 00:11:47,664
拆分成一个独立的公司
spin them off into a separate company.

231
00:11:49,959 --> 00:11:52,419
- 你不必买下整家银行  - 抱歉
- You don't buy that bank.  - I'm very sorry.

232
00:11:52,504 --> 00:11:54,421
你只需买下这家运营良好的银行就行了
You buy the good bank.

233
00:11:57,217 --> 00:11:58,717
他们对房地产不感兴趣
Look, they don't like the real estate.

234
00:11:58,802 --> 00:12:00,135
什么叫他们不感兴趣?
What do you mean, they don't like it?

235
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:03,972
Dick 我们终于有些进展了 暂时不要打扰我了
Dick, we're making real progress here, okay? Let me stay on it for now.

236
00:12:20,031 --> 00:12:22,157
Min 你好
Min, how are you?

237
00:12:22,700 --> 00:12:24,576
很高兴见到你
Great to see you.

238
00:12:25,537 --> 00:12:27,121
希望没有打扰到你们
I don't want to interrupt.

239
00:12:27,414 --> 00:12:29,540
Dick 你来得正是时候
Dick, great timing.

240
00:12:29,624 --> 00:12:32,167
看起来双方对合同的大致框架都很满意
We seem to be in sync on the broad strokes of the deal.

241
00:12:32,710 --> 00:12:34,711
我们可以回到意向书上来了吗?
Shall we get back to the letter of intent?

242
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:39,675
Min 我不得不告诉你 我觉得你正在犯一个大错
Min, I have to tell you, I think you're making a big mistake here.

243
00:12:39,843 --> 00:12:42,344
房地产资产价值巨大
There's great value in the real estate assets.

244
00:12:43,555 --> 00:12:45,514
要不通过仔细分析投资组合
How about we walk through the portfolio

245
00:12:46,182 --> 00:12:47,683
我来向你展示这一点如何?
and I'll show you?

246
00:12:50,562 --> 00:12:52,354
我们已经仔细看过了
We have looked at them.

247
00:12:52,439 --> 00:12:56,024
有些地方你肯定没看懂
Then you must have looked at them in the wrong way.

248
00:12:56,860 --> 00:12:59,653
我不想看你做出错误的决定
See, I just don't wanna see you leave money on the table.

249
00:12:59,737 --> 00:13:02,364
或许我们应该休息一下
Perhaps we should take a break.

250
00:13:08,329 --> 00:13:10,456
Min 非常抱歉
Min, I'm so sorry.

251
00:13:10,540 --> 00:13:14,668
我们一直在真心实意地进行谈判 突然就这么回到原点了?
We have negotiated in good faith. Now all of a sudden we are going backward?

252
00:13:14,752 --> 00:13:16,295
我们同意你给出的报价
We can work with you on the price.

253
00:13:16,379 --> 00:13:18,213
这与报价无关
It is not about the price.

254
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:22,009
我说的是你们处理事情的方式
It is about the way you have conducted this.

255
00:13:27,682 --> 00:13:30,642
非常感谢大家
I'd like to thank you, all of you,

256
00:13:30,935 --> 00:13:34,229
但我觉得已经没有继续谈下去的基础了
but I don't think we have a structure that works.

257
00:13:40,445 --> 00:13:41,653
什么 就这么结束了?
What, that's it?

258
00:13:41,738 --> 00:13:43,530
你们就打算这么打道回府了?
You're just gonna pack up and go back to Korea?

259
00:13:57,504 --> 00:13:59,463
- 你好  - Neel 我是Dick Fuld
- Hello?  - Neel, it's Dick Fuld.

