00:14:01,090 --> 00:14:04,718
听着 如果Hank想让我找到买家
Listen, you know, if Hank wants me to find a buyer,

261
00:14:04,802 --> 00:14:06,261
你们得出面帮我一把啊
you guys need to step up and help.

262
00:14:06,638 --> 00:14:08,931
韩国人刚刚退出交易了
The Koreans just walked out, okay?

263
00:14:09,098 --> 00:14:10,641
我只是表达一下自己的观点
Look, I'm just speaking for myself here,

264
00:14:10,725 --> 00:14:13,060
但我认为你应该做一些有利于公司的事情
but I think you need to do what's right for the firm.

265
00:14:13,144 --> 00:14:14,853
什么叫有利于?
Do what's right?

266
00:14:14,938 --> 00:14:16,438
这话是什么意思?
What is that supposed to mean?

267
00:14:16,606 --> 00:14:18,690
如果股价继续下跌
If your stock price keeps sliding,

268
00:14:18,775 --> 00:14:21,235
你也许会得到一个令人失望的报价
you may get an offer at a price that doesn't look all that compelling,

269
00:14:21,319 --> 00:14:24,279
但为了公司的持续经营 你必须接受它
but you may have to take it just to keep the company intact.

270
00:14:24,697 --> 00:14:26,031
你指什么样的买价?
What kind of price are you talking about?

271
00:14:26,282 --> 00:14:27,699
可能会...
Could be...

272
00:14:27,784 --> 00:14:30,077
我指 股价可能在个位数
I mean, it might be low single digits.

273
00:14:32,664 --> 00:14:36,333
二月份 我们公司每股66美元
Last February, we were at 66 a share.

274
00:14:38,336 --> 00:14:42,589
雷曼兄弟可不是贝尔斯登
Lehman Brothers is not Bear Stearns.

275
00:14:42,674 --> 00:14:46,134
我们业绩很好的 房地产会复苏的
We've got a great business. Real estate's gonna come back.

276
00:14:46,261 --> 00:14:49,263
我他妈不会把这公司送人的!
I am not fucking giving this company away!

277
00:14:49,764 --> 00:14:51,008
在雷曼兄弟股价因其
While the real estate market has put

